Maintainer: Tobias Mildenberger <tobm@dtu.dk>
Description: A movement model that allows estimation of habitat preferences and
    fine-scale movement rates based on advection-diffusion models using various
    types of tagging data. It supports flexible spatiotemporal modeling with
    options for Kalman filter or matrix exponential approaches, and includes
    tools for data preparation, model fitting, and visualisation.
